h2 General purpose

dl
	dt watch
	dd watch source files for changes and rebuild relevant output files

	dt livereload
	dd do livereload on file changes

	dt sprockets
	dd concat css and js files in sprockets-like way: <code>/*= require ... */</code> and <code>/*= require_tree ... */</code>

	dt globals
	dd allows to prepend file contents into all other files.


